ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectGovernment of Canada and the Government of the British Virgin Islands ** Agreement for the exchange of information on tax matters **
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Foreign Affairs to sign, or to delegate powers to sign, on behalf of Canada, subject to ratification, the AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the GOVERNMENT OF THE BRITISH VIRGIN ISLANDS under entrustment from the GOVERNMENT OF THE UNITED KINGDOM OF GREAT BRITAIN AND NORTHERN IRELAND for the exchange of information on TAX MATTERS.
